      "description": "Offered for sale is a good-condition example that has clearly been kept up better than the average older car and presents as a solid, enjoyable driver. It is not a mint or show-level vehicle, but it is a clean, honest car that should appeal to someone looking for a well-maintained example rather than a project. Expect the normal cosmetic wear, small imperfections, and signs of age that come with an older vehicle, but overall it shows well, feels cared for, and should make a satisfying driver for its next owner.",
